          <li class="flex items-top mb-2"><svg class="inline-block mr-3 h-7 w-3 flex-none fill-current" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" height="24px" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="24px" fill="#000000"><path d="M0 0h24v24H0z" fill="none"/><path d="M12 2C6.47 2 2 6.47 2 12s4.47 10 10 10 10-4.47 10-10S17.53 2 12 2z"/></svg>Foster new opportunities for collaboration.</li>
          <li class="flex items-top mb-2"><svg class="inline-block mr-3 h-7 w-3 flex-none fill-current" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" height="24px" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="24px" fill="#000000"><path d="M0 0h24v24H0z" fill="none"/><path d="M12 2C6.47 2 2 6.47 2 12s4.47 10 10 10 10-4.47 10-10S17.53 2 12 2z"/></svg>Support, facilitate and grow arts & cultural events.</li>
          <li class="flex items-top mb-2"><svg class="inline-block mr-3 h-7 w-3 flex-none fill-current" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" height="24px" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="24px" fill="#000000"><path d="M0 0h24v24H0z" fill="none"/><path d="M12 2C6.47 2 2 6.47 2 12s4.47 10 10 10 10-4.47 10-10S17.53 2 12 2z"/></svg>Advocate for arts-centered development.</li>
          <li class="flex items-top mb-2"><svg class="inline-block mr-3 h-7 w-3 flex-none fill-current" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" height="24px" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="24px" fill="#000000"><path d="M0 0h24v24H0z" fill="none"/><path d="M12 2C6.47 2 2 6.47 2 12s4.47 10 10 10 10-4.47 10-10S17.53 2 12 2z"/></svg>Establish a thriving creative hub.</li>
          <li class="flex items-top mb-2"><svg class="inline-block mr-3 h-7 w-3 flex-none fill-current" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" height="24px" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="24px" fill="#000000"><path d="M0 0h24v24H0z" fill="none"/><path d="M12 2C6.47 2 2 6.47 2 12s4.47 10 10 10 10-4.47 10-10S17.53 2 12 2z"/></svg>Provide for economic stabilization.</li>
          <li class="flex items-top mb-2"><svg class="inline-block mr-3 h-7 w-3 flex-none fill-current" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" height="24px" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="24px" fill="#000000"><path d="M0 0h24v24H0z" fill="none"/><path d="M12 2C6.47 2 2 6.47 2 12s4.47 10 10 10 10-4.47 10-10S17.53 2 12 2z"/></svg>Preserve cultural diversity and artistic character.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
